68
00:04:50,248 --> 00:04:52,499
Dad, look!
- No, no, no!

69
00:04:52,583 --> 00:04:54,876
Ryan, do not touch him, please!

70
00:04:55,295 --> 00:04:56,837
Oh, no, no, no, no, get him away!

71
00:04:56,921 --> 00:04:59,172
