No, no! Get away, get away! Go!

74
00:05:05,054 --> 00:05:06,596
Okay. Oh, no, no, no.

75
00:05:06,681 --> 00:05:08,098
- He's thirsty.
- No, no, no.

76
00:05:08,182 --> 00:05:11,059
No, you don't! There we go.

77
00:05:11,144 --> 00:05:12,602
Well, Ryan, he's a stray.

78
00:05:12,687 --> 00:05:14,313
If we give him water,
he's just going to come back.

79
00:05:14,397 --> 00:05:17,774
Come on, Dad, why can't we keep him?
I mean, we've got a new house.

80
00:05:17,859 --> 00:05:19,818
