He asked if we could all pray together.

91
00:05:54,145 --> 00:05:56,855
Really? What did you pray about?

92
00:05:56,939 --> 00:05:59,024
He met a dog.
What do you think he prayed for?

93
00:06:01,069 --> 00:06:03,820
Just a walking petri dish, that dog.

94
00:06:03,905 --> 00:06:06,073
And Jordan was very precise.

95
00:06:06,157 --> 00:06:09,951
He prayed for good visibility, good weather
on the hiking trip tomorrow.

96
00:06:10,036 --> 00:06:13,288
The hiking trip? Oh, right. Yeah.
The hiking trip. Yeah, yeah, yeah.

97
00:06:13,373 --> 00:06:15,248
You wanna know what I prayed for?

98
00:06:15,333 --> 00:06:17,209
Yeah. What did you pray for?

99
00:06:17,293 --> 00:06:20,420
