as a family.

100
00:06:21,589 --> 00:06:26,009
Honey, you don't need to pray for that
to happen. I will make that happen.

101
00:06:27,595 --> 00:06:31,932
- What would you pray for?
- Me? I don't know. Praying just...

102
00:06:33,810 --> 00:06:37,646
Honey, you're the one who said
you wanted to change the world.

103
00:06:38,147 --> 00:06:40,065
It's a pretty big job.

104
00:06:40,358 --> 00:06:43,151
If it were me,
I would take all the help I could get.

105
00:06:48,157 --> 00:06:51,201
Former Buffalo News
anchor, Evan Baxter, takes office tomorrow

106
00:06:51,285 --> 00:06:53,703
to make good on a lofty campaign promise.

107
00:06:53,788 --> 00:06:56,248
- What are we going to do?
Change the world!

108
00:06:56,332 --> 00:06:59,793
Good luck, Congressman.
Many have tried, many have failed.

109
00:06:59,877 --> 00:07:03,046
- Hello!
- This is Regina Sparks reporting for...

110
00:07:20,481 --> 00:07:22,315
