Yeah.

130
00:09:36,993 --> 00:09:38,243
- Bye. See you.
- Good luck, honey.

131
00:09:38,327 --> 00:09:39,452
- Bye, guys!
- See you later.

132
00:09:39,537 --> 00:09:40,537
Later, gator.

133
00:09:42,582 --> 00:09:43,873
Oh, gosh.

134
00:09:43,958 --> 00:09:46,668
Wow. Honey, did you order anything?

135
00:09:47,044 --> 00:09:49,170
"Alpha and Omega Hardware"?

136
00:09:49,255 --> 00:09:51,673
