- Me either.

137
00:09:52,008 --> 00:09:53,842
What do we have?

138
00:09:55,344 --> 00:09:57,053
What is this stuff?

139
00:09:58,472 --> 00:10:00,307
Must have the wrong address.

140
00:10:00,933 --> 00:10:02,726
Yup. The wrong address.

141
00:10:04,979 --> 00:10:06,563
Congressman Baxter.
Good morning.

142
00:10:06,647 --> 00:10:07,606
Good morning.

143
00:10:07,690 --> 00:10:09,024
Good morning, Congressman Baxter.
- Hello.

144
00:10:09,108 --> 00:10:11,526
Good morning, Congressman Baxter.
- Good morning.

145
00:10:11,611 --> 00:10:14,613
Oh, this is so cool.

146
00:10:17,825 --> 00:10:19,618
Yeah. This'll work.

147
00:10:19,702 --> 00:10:23,538
There he is! The head honcho.
The big kahuna.

148
00:10:23,623 --> 00:10:25,624
Rita, I think I have to do the dance.

149
00:10:25,708 --> 00:10:26,875
Do the dance.

150
00:10:30,463 --> 00:10:31,796
That's enough of the dance.

151
00:10:31,881 --> 00:10:33,965
Oh, this is nice! This is really nice!

152
00:10:34,050 --> 00:10:36,718
