154
00:10:38,095 --> 00:10:39,971
- Congressman!
- Hey, Marty!

155
00:10:40,056 --> 00:10:41,473
- Nice sound to that.
- I like it.

156
00:10:41,557 --> 00:10:42,557
Here they are!

157
00:10:43,726 --> 00:10:44,809
All right.

158
00:10:44,894 --> 00:10:46,645
You remember Sarah, Allen, Michael.

159
00:10:46,729 --> 00:10:49,397
