Eugene Tennanbaum. I found him at G.W.

160
00:10:49,482 --> 00:10:51,149
Sort of a walking search engine. Watch this.

161
00:10:51,233 --> 00:10:53,485
- How many stars on the flag in 1818?
-15.

162
00:10:53,569 --> 00:10:55,487
