165
00:11:00,576 --> 00:11:03,244
Very impressive.
A little freaky, but I like this kid.

166
00:11:03,537 --> 00:11:04,913
I love you.

167
00:11:07,416 --> 00:11:10,752
I mean, we should hang out socially.
I just got a ping-pong table.

168
00:11:10,836 --> 00:11:12,504
Not going to happen.

169
00:11:12,588 --> 00:11:15,840
Go find out where his license plates are.
Everybody else, back to your holes.

170
00:11:15,925 --> 00:11:18,802
He was actually right.
- I'm doing a background check on that kid.

171
00:11:18,886 --> 00:11:23,556
Ta-da! This, my friend, is a power office,
to remind you of the mission!

172
00:11:23,641 --> 00:11:25,058
"Change the world!"

173
00:11:25,142 --> 00:11:26,851
- Okay, Evan, who do you know?
- What do you mean?

174
00:11:26,936 --> 00:11:28,853
Oh, come on.
Yesterday we're in the basement.

175
00:11:28,938 --> 00:11:30,855
Today, look at this place.
It's like the Emerald City!

176
00:11:30,940 --> 00:11:34,192
"Enjoy your office.
Your neighbor, Congressman Long. "

177
00:11:34,276 --> 00:11:36,361
