195
00:12:18,529 --> 00:12:20,613
All right, Eugene, Congressman Long's bill.
What is it?

196
00:12:20,698 --> 00:12:23,575
HR7124, better known as CINPLAN.

197
00:12:23,659 --> 00:12:26,327
The bill would open up fringe areas
of the national parks for development.

198
00:12:26,412 --> 00:12:27,912
Long's been sitting on it for ages...

199
00:12:27,997 --> 00:12:29,956
Got it. Pause. Come on, Evan, this is huge.

200
00:12:30,040 --> 00:12:31,541
You hitch your wagon to the right star,

201
00:12:31,625 --> 00:12:33,752
you could ride all the way down
to Pennsylvania Avenue.

202
00:12:33,836 --> 00:12:35,170
This is day one.

203
00:12:35,254 --> 00:12:37,422
You got your name on a major piece
of legislation!

204
00:12:37,506 --> 00:12:40,341
And another thing,
he wants you to read it today.

205
00:12:40,634 --> 00:12:42,135
Well, I can't do it today.

206
00:12:42,219 --> 00:12:43,303
- I promised my kids...
- Eugene.

207
00:12:43,387 --> 00:12:45,430
Well, sir, there's a time clock on the bill.

208
00:12:45,514 --> 00:12:47,599
If Congressman Long wants to pass it
this quarter,

209
00:12:47,683 --> 00:12:49,809
he's going to have to introduce it
to the committee immediately.

210
00:12:49,894 --> 00:12:52,395
I'm personally going with
whatever Congressman Baxter decides,

211
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:55,440
because if I could be like one man,
it'd be him.

212
00:12:55,524 --> 00:12:56,858
Either him or Kareem.

213
00:12:56,942 --> 00:12:59,194
- Can I tase him?
- Gene! Heel!

214
00:12:59,278 --> 00:13:00,695
